title: Class - Outdoor-Floor and Table lamps
description: Taking its cue from early 20th century design, the Class floor lamp brings the refined, intimate aesthetic of a patio light with the functional performance of a bollard. Rather than silently integrating into the garden environment, the Class outdoor lamp stands handsome and proud, its cylindrical glass luminaire radiating with a soft, diffuse light. LED strip lighting with dimming control is encased within each tube.
